The,Paylike,API,allows,developers,to,accept,payments,online,using,Visa,or,MasterCard,Paylike,is,an,online,payment,service,that,works,with,any,screen,or,device,including,mobile,devices,and,tablets,Paylike,can,handle,both,single,and,recurring,transactions,in,currencies,Paylike,provides,payment,links,a,virtual,POS,and,a,complete,test,environment,for,integration